We are using Next.js 15.3.2 which came out after your knowledge cutoff please refer to the Next.js docs at:

https://nextjs.org/docs

Make sure to pay attention to the asynchronous way we should be handling params. Use 'async', destructuring, and await where possible to reference the data: 

```javascript
async function Page({ params }) {
  // asynchronous access of `params.id`.
  const { id } = await params
  return <p>ID: {id}</p>
}
```

We are using TailwindCss Version 4. It does not require a configuration file. The framework has been extended directly into css. Please refer to the docs:
https://tailwindcss.com/docs

We are using shadcn/ui for the design of this application. Please use Shadcn/ui for components when possible. please refer to the docs:
https://ui.shadcn.com/docs